@2209 = ~Wind Wall~
@2210 = ~Wind Wall
(Alteration)
Level: 3
Range: 10 yards/level
Duration: 1 round/level
Casting Time: 3
Area of Effect: wall, 10 x 5 feet/level, 2 feet wide
Saving Throw: None

