@23900 = ~aTWEAKS - Simple Cleric/Paladin script~
@23901 = ~This script will allow a Cleric/Paladin to turn undead whenever he is idle. By default the Cleric/Paladin will only use turning when undead opponents are nearby and stop once they are out of his line of sight. Pressing the 'D' key toggles this setting and causes the Cleric/Paladin to turn undead constantly, regardless of enemy presence. Note that the Cleric/Paladin won't attack opponents nor defend himself while turning undead. Pressing the 'V' key toggles this setting and causes the Cleric/Paladin to stop turning undead and start attacking the nearest enemy. Pressing the 'V' key a second time causes the character to attack any non-undead creatures on-sight and automatically switch to turning whenever an undead creature is encountered. Lastly, pressing the 'E' key will instruct the Cleric/Paladin to heal injured party members. By default, the Cleric/Paladin will only heal allies outside of combat. Pressing the 'E' key again can force the Cleric/Paladin to heal allies even during combat or turn off the healing routine completely. This script will never override player-assigned actions. (RR#CLP01)~
